&lt;li&gt;You’ll work closely with product managers, designers and engineers to develop key product success metrics, to set targets, to measure results and outcomes, and to size opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’ll design, build and update end-to-end data pipelines, working closely with stakeholders to drive the collection of new data and the refinement of existing data sources and tables.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’ll partner closely with product researchers to build a holistic understanding of our customers, our products and our business.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’ll influence our product roadmap and product strategy through exploratory analysis and quantitative research&lt;/li&gt;
